Insurance Industries Extension Integration

Enable the Insurance Industries Extension package and learn about a mapping interface that lets Vlocity policy services work with the Salesforce FSC Insurance Policy data model.

Enable Insurance Industries Extension
The Insurance Industries Extension package is an add-on application that requires Financial Services Cloud (FSC) licenses from Salesforce. Before you can use it, you need to enable it.
The InsPolicy FSC-Vlocity Mapping Interface
The InsPolicy interface is a generic service interface that lets Vlocity policy services work with any policy data model, including the Salesforce FSC Insurance Policy data model.
title: Enable Insurance Industries Extension Integration
